definitions.definition: A hamlet and civil parish in Cumberland , Cumbria , England , previously in Copeland borough ( OS grid ref NY0505 ) .
A suburb of Auckland , New Zealand .
Former name of Boileau , Quebec , Canada .
A rural community in Centre Wellington , Ontario , Canada .
